{
  "title": "Xtra Tangy Peruvian Strawberry Wrap",
  "description": "A tangy and refreshing Peruvian dish featuring strawberries and shio-cure, wrapped in a corn husk, perfect for a light lunch or snack. This Mediterranean-friendly wrap is a unique twist on traditional Peruvian cuisine.",
  "cuisine": "Peruvian",
